就医，我们也会及时转介到医院，希望能减少此事对孩子造成的身心伤害。」 22 日上午，受害女孩的父亲王彪（化名）也告诉北青报记者，21 日晚，妇联和公安主动上门看望、关怀了孩子。13 岁少女被邻居性侵，4 名嫌疑人全部归案 来源：北京青年报"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-e830817ed2e0093885ae96a885596fd3_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "70 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/602337774"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIvcGfhca369Y6EAMaCDk2MTMzMzQ2IIjOq6MGMAk4tgFAD3IJNjAyMzM3Nzc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1684764169.2917151", "card_id": "Q_312151810", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 33}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "父母小时候对你很坏很坏，长大了突然对你很好。你该怎么办？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-ff8485907bc625b11a63f369116f8d3a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/312151810"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IvcGfhca369Y6EAMaCDMxNjQzNzY1ILLHkOMFMAA4OkAQcgkzMTIxNTE4MTB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1684764169.2922215", "card_id": "Q_597596223", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 334}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "想知道大家都是因为什么熬夜?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-effe420150489ce80dd8f734f3a786a3_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "63 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "